# Prefer MatrAIx product language

Do **not** use the phrases or branding:

- "persona eval"
- "persona-eval"
- `persona_eval`
- "PersonaEval"

Use MatrAIx / Playground / Harbor / chatbot / survey / os-app language instead.

Host-only standalone compose for chatbot sidecars lives under
``.playground_sidecar/`` (not any `persona_eval*` path). Prefer names like
`chatbot sidecar`, `local compose`, or `.playground_sidecar` when documenting
or adding new identifiers.
